    <item>
      <title>以色列需要更多士兵，因为预备役军人厌倦了持续不断的战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/israel-needs-more-soldiers-as-reservists-tire-of-constant-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自以色列与哈马斯爆发战争以来，约夫·阿多米已经在陆军预备役服役近六个月，抛下了妻子、孩子和在特拉维夫的保险技术工作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/israel-needs-more-soldiers-as-reservists-tire-of-constant-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波罗的海国家敦促北约加强防空以抵御俄罗斯威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/baltics-urge-bolstered-nato-air-defense-against-russia-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱沙尼亚最高国防官员呼吁北约加强与俄罗斯接壤成员国的防空能力，因为北约严重缺乏远程反导能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/baltics-urge-bolstered-nato-air-defense-against-russia-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>利益分歧致加拿大质疑“亚洲北约”构想</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/canada-doubts-idea-of-asian-nato-amid-diverging-interests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大国防部长比尔·布莱尔对“亚洲版北约”的想法表示怀疑。他表示，由于该地区战略利益各异，任何以美国为首的军事联盟都会显得不同。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/canada-doubts-idea-of-asian-nato-amid-diverging-interests</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 02:22:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>党内元老退却，日本领导人之争悬而未决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/japan-s-leadership-race-is-wide-open-as-party-elders-retreat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本执政党领袖竞选于周四拉开帷幕，由于党内元老的控制力减弱，创纪录数量的候选人可以参与公开竞选，以带领国家度过关键的过渡期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/japan-s-leadership-race-is-wide-open-as-party-elders-retreat</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 00:10:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国称朝鲜发射疑似弹道导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/n-korea-launches-suspected-ballistic-missile-s-korea-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国军方称，朝鲜周四凌晨在其东海岸发射了多枚短程弹道导弹。几天前，朝鲜领导人金正恩誓言要大幅增强其核武器能力，并让军队做好战斗准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/n-korea-launches-suspected-ballistic-missile-s-korea-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 22:36:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>报告称英国 NHS 资金缺口达 370 亿英镑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/england-s-nhs-broken-by-37-billion-investment-gap-ara-darzi-s-report-finds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一份报告指出，英格兰国民健康服务体系 (NHS) 因缺乏资金而陷入瘫痪已逾 10 年，该报告揭示了新任首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 在重建这个根植于国民精神的组织时所面临的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/england-s-nhs-broken-by-37-billion-investment-gap-ara-darzi-s-report-finds</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 21:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经济学家称泰国新总理的改革议程缺乏具体内容</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/new-thai-pm-s-reform-blueprint-lacks-specifics-economists-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国新任总理制定了应对最紧迫问题的路线图，包括接近创纪录的家庭债务、低迷的经济增长和老龄化社会。但经济学家认为，该计划缺乏确保在规定时间内取得成果的细节。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/new-thai-pm-s-reform-blueprint-lacks-specifics-economists-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国与菲律宾在谈判中对新海域热点提出主权要求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/china-philippines-hold-talks-as-new-hotspot-emerges-in-sea-row</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国和菲律宾在周三的外交官会议上坚持对南海新热点地区提出各自主权要求，尽管双方都在寻求缓解紧张局势的方法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/china-philippines-hold-talks-as-new-hotspot-emerges-in-sea-row</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 16:51:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以下是日本下一任领导人的九位候选人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/who-could-replace-kishida-candidates-who-could-be-japan-s-new-prime-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[9 月 27 日，日本执政党自民党将举行领导人选举，将有创纪录的 9 名候选人参选。由于自民党在议会中占据主导地位，此次选举几乎肯定会产生日本下一任首相。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/who-could-replace-kishida-candidates-who-could-be-japan-s-new-prime-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 02:41:28 GMT</pubDate>
